data.description: Beautifully updated 3 bedroom, 2 bath home with a 2 car garage, located in the desirable Parkdale area of Waco, TX!  This home has been lovingly maintained over the years with updates including wood look tile floors throughout the entire home, can lighting, HVAC 2017, extra insulation 2018, privacy fence & storage shed 2020, & gutters with leaf guards.  This floor plan features a comfortable living area and oversized dining space with built-in china hutch, plus a flex space between the two to use as a sitting area or play space. The kitchen has been nicely updated and features a gas stove, microwave, dishwasher, pantry & refrigerator. You have accommodating bedrooms throughout with great closet space for storage and the primary bedroom has an en suite with shower.  Outdoors, in the privacy fenced backyard, you have an expansive back patio, perfect for enjoying evenings at home. Don't miss your opportunity to call this beauty HOME!
